</span><span class='line'><span class="no">Requests</span> <span class="n">per</span> <span class="ss">second</span><span class="p">:</span>    <span class="mi">2245</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="mi">57</span> <span class="o">[</span><span class="c1">#/sec] (mean)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="no">Time</span> <span class="n">per</span> <span class="ss">request</span><span class="p">:</span>       <span class="mi">0</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="mi">445</span> <span class="o">[</span><span class="n">ms</span><span class="o">]</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">mean</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="no">Time</span> <span class="n">per</span> <span class="ss">request</span><span class="p">:</span>       <span class="mi">0</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="mi">445</span> <span class="o">[</span><span class="n">ms</span><span class="o">]</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">mean</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">across</span> <span class="n">all</span> <span class="n">concurrent</span> <span class="n">requests</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="no">Transfer</span> <span class="ss">rate</span><span class="p">:</span>          <span class="mi">997</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="mi">79</span> <span class="o">[</span><span class="no">Kbytes</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">sec</span><span class="o">]</span> <span class="n">received</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="sr">/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="sr">&lt;p&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p>以上是两个服务器在没有任何调优的情况下的测试结果,通过数据不难发现，nginx的请求量/每秒基本比apache多了1/3,可见nginx不是一般的快,这就是为什么我使用nginx的原因。</p>
]]></content>
